** Want to bring ideas to life? **   
  
  
  
You're in the right place. If you're looking for a fresh challenge, why choose
Aurecon? It comes down to one, crucial question. What kind of world do you
want to create for the next generation? Truth is, the decisions being made
right now will determine the future of everything - from the local community
to the entire planet. One of those decisions is: who do you decide to work
for?  
  
  
  
** How will your ideas contribute to shaping what's next? **   
  
  
  
We are seeking a Senior AI Developer and technical team leader to join our
technology group. You will work on developing and implementing Generative AI
solutions to transform processes and decision-making across our design,
engineering and advisory operations.  
  
  
  
Here are the key things you will do to 'bring ideas to life'.

  * Design, develop and deploy AI solutions that solve real problems such as optimizing design options, streamlining engineering workflows, improving project planning and scheduling, and more. 
  * Lead AI product development, mentor junior staff and foster code quality and collaboration. 
  * Work closely with business leaders and end users across departments to identify opportunities where AI can drive process improvements and enhance decision making. 
  * Rapidly prototype and pilot AI solutions in our fast-paced, agile solution development environment. 
  * Take ownership of AI products from design through deployment, testing and maintenance. 
  * Maintain and continuously improve existing AI models and systems to utilize new data, techniques, and technologies. 
  * Participate in architecture reviews and provide recommendations for implementing production-ready AI solutions aligned to industry best practices. 
  * Stay up to date on the latest AI research and technologies that may benefit the organisation. 

  
  
** How will your future be shaped by us? **   
  
  
  
Joining Aurecon means you'll be at the award-winning edge of innovation and
sustainability. AFR ranked us Top 5 among sustainability leaders and Top 3 of
all innovative companies in professional services. One Consult awarded us an
innovative design award. Plus, we were Consult Australia's large firm of the
year.  
  
  
  
You really can bring your whole self to work and be confident your voice will
be heard. We don't just claim we're inclusive and innovative, as proven by the
independent awards and accreditations we've gained. We've been recognised for
our innovation culture, gender equality and our LGBTI+ inclusion. Plus, we
have a robust Reconciliation Action Plan - our fourth edition since 2014.  
  
On a personal level you'll have access to flexible work hours, remote work,
working holidays, part-time and job share options. You'll continue to grow,
thanks to learning and development opportunities that further your eminence,
leadership, and professional accreditations. Outside of work, you'll be
further supported with competitive paid parental leave, cultural public
holiday swaps, plus wellbeing support programmes.  
  
  
  
** What are we looking for from you? **   
  
  
  
You'll have a genuine passion for re-imagining problems and continuous
learning to help shape the future.  
  
We value that each of our team members brings something different to Aurecon.
We look for people who have had a broad range of experiences throughout their
career and can demonstrate how they have worked as part of a team to bring
ideas to life.  
  
As well as experience in a similar role, you will need:  
  
  

  * MS/PhD in Computer Science, AI, Machine Learning, or related technical field 
  * Strong experience building and deploying machine learning systems in production environments. 
  * Demonstrated ability to lead and mentor technical teams. 
  * Expertise in languages and frameworks like Python, PyTorch, Langchain, etc 
  * Experience applying techniques like computer vision, NLP, or reinforcement learning etc to real-world problems. 
  * Cloud platform experience (AWS/Azure/GCP) 
  * Ability to clearly communicate complex technical concepts to senior leadership. 
  * Passion for leveraging AI technology to transform and disrupt how we work and how we deliver for our clients. 

  
  
